<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Outlook Sync Latencies and Errors>
We are investigating increased WorkMail Outlook synchronization latencies and error rates in the US-EAST-1 Region impacting the sending and receiving of new messages or appointments in Outlook clients.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Outlook Sync Latencies and Errors>
Between 11:06 AM and 12:09 PM PDT we experienced increased WorkMail Outlook synchronization latencies and error rates in the US-EAST-1 Region, impacting the sending and receiving of new messages or appointments in Outlook clients. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
